		</div>
		<div
			class="w-[70px] h-[70px] flex items-center justify-center border border-gray-400 rounded-xl hover:text-White-Principal hover:bg-Violet-text transition duration-300 ease-in-out"
		>
			<a
				href="https://linkedin.com/in/tuusuario"
				target="_blank"
